{"tid":527820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國文青呢個字好戇鳩？","createTime":"2018-01-13T05:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T11:11:45.000Z","uid":143499,"like":56,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e0cf4a7089809250e6b76a6ba6fec0f9a3688fb4","tid":527820,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"細細個文青係解一啲有文學修養嘅人， 俾人嘅印象會係朱自清、魯迅依啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到近幾年， 文青比我嘅印象係一班著到鬼五馬六， 一半mk一半嬉皮士冇料扮四表嘅厹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其是係文青眼鏡真係好鳩撚柒， 唔係人人都carry到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n週街都有人帶， 尤其是啲死肥婆塊面脹到成個月餅盒咁， 再載幼框文青眼鏡， 真係好撚想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有啲契弟成日影埋啲out fo嘅相， 曬相嗰陣又落埋啲奇怪藥水， 搞到幅相好似中咗輻射咁， 然後就話成件事好文青好有品味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係隔咗咁耐係連登從來冇見過人批評呢個現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcd1b75b024886ff9bbf123f77f2f502860e279","tid":527820,"uid":28726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"唔係鬧咗好耐喇咩"},{"pid":"68dd6db538e4327f4ab88b087663c7abc5b53b8f","tid":527820,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"法唔法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5f0a1a9831f62294acb5076e793df3a8d1e42b","tid":527820,"uid":97226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"啱啱放咗出黎冇耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d610e8afcbc1a4e9dce6a0f0e7e704a1711637","tid":527820,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9fcd1b75b024886ff9bbf123f77f2f502860e279","tid":527820,"uid":28726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"唔係鬧咗好耐喇咩"},"cite